  #others
    %h3 Other Websites
    %p The Service may contain links to other websites which are outside our control and are not covered by this Policy. If you access other websites using the links provided, the operators of these websites may collect information from you which will be used by them in accordance with their privacy policy, which may differ from ours.

    = link_to 'back to top', '#top', class: 'top_link'

  #international
    %h3 International Transfers
    %p In some instances we may have to transfer your personal information to third parties located outside of the European Union for the purposes stated in this Policy. In such cases we shall ensure that appropriate provisions are in place, as per the requirements of applicable laws, to ensure that your personal information is appropriately protected.

    = link_to 'back to top', '#top', class: 'top_link'

  #access
    %h3 Access to Information
    %p Please contact us if you would like to know what information we are storing about you or to ask us to make any necessary changes to ensure that your information is accurate and kept up to date. We may ask for proof of identity before providing you with any information requested and reserve the right to refuse to provide information if identity is not established.

  %p Any changes to this Policy will be posted on the Website [and Apps].

  If you have any further comments or questions regarding our User Agreements then please contact us - we're ready to help.

